title: Malware - Tipos y cómo proteger tu PC
description:
Malware - Tipos y cómo proteger tu PC

Malware es el término utilizado para identificar programas maliciosos o dañinos para tu PC. El malware es un software que está destinado a dañar o deshabilitar computadoras y sistemas informáticos. Para luchar contra el malware y proteger tu computadora, necesitas usar herramientas como antivirus, anti spywares y firewalls; muchos de los cuales se pueden encontrar de forma gratuita en la web. También hay suites de seguridad completas disponibles para integrar a tu computadora Dell, lo que facilita enormemente la protección de tu sistema.

En este video hablaremos de los más comunes, cómo infectan tu computadora y cómo mantenerte protegido. 

Aquí te mostramos algunos de los principales tipos de software maliciosos que pueden causar problemas importantes a tu sistema informático.

00:00 Malware qué es y cuáles son los tipos de Malware
00:46 Virus
01:02 Worms o Gusanos
01:20 Troyanos
01:40 Spyware
01:59 Adware
02:15 Ransomware

Virus
Un virus es un programa de capaz de autorreplicarse. Una vez que una computadora está infectada con un virus, éste puede propagarse a muchos otros archivos de tu computadora. Los virus se pueden propagar muy fácilmente por Internet a través de la descargas de archivos.

Worms o Gusanos
Un Worm es un tipo de malware ligeramente diferente. Al igual que los virus, pueden auto-replicarse, pero los gusanos son capaces de enviarse a sí mismos a muchas personas diferentes. Son muy peligrosos y pueden propagarse automáticamente enviando mensajes a las personas de tu lista de contactos.

Troyanos
Un troyano técnicamente no es un virus porque normalmente no puede hacer copias de sí mismo. Algunos troyanos se auto replican, pero generalmente son aplicaciones aparentemente útiles que has instalado que pueden abrir una puerta trasera secreta desde donde los hackers pueden ingresar y robar tu información. La mayoría de las veces no tienes idea de que estás infectado con un troyano.

Spyware
El spyware es similar a un troyano, pero en lugar de permitir que un pirata informático acceda a tu PC, lo espía silenciosamente. El spyware puede robar los números de tu tarjeta de crédito, información de tu cuenta bancaria y cualquier otra información confidencial y personal que tengas en tu computadora. A menudo está incluido con software de procedencia desconocida  para que se instale sin que te des cuenta.

Adware
Adware es básicamente lo mismo que Spyware, aunque no siempre es tan malicioso. Se instala en tu computadora e intenta mostrarte anuncios o publicidad relevante y de forma agresiva. Muchos de estos muestran tantos anuncios que pueden ralentizar su PC.
Cómo Eliminar Adware de tu Navegador: https://dell.to/3s1UzVA 

Ransomware
El Ransomware amenaza con publicar tus datos o bloquea continuamente el acceso a ellos a menos que se pague un rescate. Mientras que algunos ransomware simples pueden bloquear el sistema pero no requiere mucho para desbloquearlo, otros ransomwares más avanzados usan una técnica llamada "extorsión viral criptográfica" que encripta los archivos de la víctima, haciéndolos virtualmente inaccesibles.

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'.

title: Aca Lukas - Zašto plačeš mila majko? | Pesma iz filma ,,Kafana na Balkanu'' (OFFICIAL VIDEO)
description:
https://m.imdb.com/title/tt29281792/

Prodaja karata: https://tickets.rs/event/aca_lukas_4654

,,Zašto plačeš mila Majko’’ pesma je iz filma ,,Kafana na Balkanu’’ koja je rađena po životu najveće balkanske zvezde Aleksandra Vukasnovića - Ace Lukasa! Do premijere filma 3.11. u Štark Areni uživajte uz ,,Zašto plačeš mila majko’’ 

U suret događaju koji nije viđen na našim prostorima, a predstavlja amalgam nezabeleženo dobrog multimedijalnog projekta, svetske produkcije i fantastičnog sadržaja - premijera filma "Kafana na Balkanu", a potom koncert Ace Lukasa i Folk Haus Benda 3.11.2023. godine u Štark Areni, Hype produkcija vam predstavlja novu numeru najveće balkanske zvezde Ace Lukasa, "Zašto plačeš mila majko" koja je dostupna na Hype Jutjub kanalu.

Pesma je od prve do poslednje note satkana od čiste emocije, a zanimljiva je činjenica da je Aca Lukas pisao, komponovao i aranžirao ovu numeru, kao i još nekoliko novih numera koje ćete imati priliku da čujete u filmu "Kafana na Balkanu" koji nastaje po motivima života Ace Lukasa i demistifikuje sve detalje iz njegovog privatnog i profesionalnog segmenta života. Pesma "Zašto plačeš mila majko" prati životni put i prekretnicu glavnog protagoniste Peđe kojeg igra glumac Mladen Sovilj.

Saša Mirković, direktor i vlasnik Hype produkcije zajedno sa svojim timom prikazaće publici jedan potpuno novi koncept događaja, a sve što vi treba da uradite, jeste da se spremite za jedno filmično, emotivno i muzičko putovanje.

비투비 (BTOB) - '나의 바람 (Wind And Wish)' Official Music Video
description:
비투비 (BTOB) - '나의 바람 (Wind And Wish)' Official Music Video

Composed by 임현식, 손영진(MosPick)
Lyrics by 임현식, 손영진(MosPick), 이민혁 (HUTA), 프니엘
Arranged by 임현식, 손영진(MosPick)

당신의 행복을 바라고 행운을 빌어요 = 사랑

누군가의 행복을 바라는 바람을 불어오는 바람에 전하는 중의적인 의미를 담았으며, 그동안 사랑받아왔던 비투비 표 발라드/댄스곡이 종합적으로 느껴지는 대중적인 곡이다.

차가운 바람이 스칠 때 그대는 따뜻하기를 바란다.

Wish for your happiness and wish you good luck = Love

The title “Wind And Wish” came from the Korean word BARAM (Romanized for 바람) into two different ideas of Wishing (BARAM for “Wish”) someone’s happiness to a blowing wind (BARAM for “Wind”) as an ambiguity. Meanwhile, it brings out once again a form of BTOB’s very own ballad+dance song that every listener loved.

When the cold wind passes you by, wish you will stay warm.

#吳青峰
#戀人絮語
#馬拉美的星期二

關於創作人與創作的關係
關於戀人以及那些叨叨絮語

Follow Qing Feng
Instagram | https://www.instagram.com/imqingfeng
Facebook | https://www.facebook.com/WuQingFeng
Weibo | https://www.weibo.com/u/1822796164
YouTube | http://bit.ly/qingyoutube


創作，是遇見，是被理解，是戀愛，是結合。
文：吳青峰

你會不會在一些黑暗的時刻，想找個人說話，翻了翻通訊，沒有一個人名可以讓你投遞出訊息，最後還是沉默？

會有那麼一瞬間，一個人，一句話，一首歌，一件事，讓你好像得到了可以休息的地方，揭開你看不見的盲點，幫你看看你哪裡受傷。當你心裡只有累，他可以讓你把累拆開來讀讀看，發現將「累」寫作「田糸」，讀起來竟是甜蜜。

我常常是在心裡冒出音符或文字時，有這樣的心情。啊，或許我最需要的，是自己的擁抱，而那些或許是浮出的靈感，或許是貓咪的一個撒嬌，或許是溫柔的一句話，打開了我的窗口。

於是凝固的心開始通風、流動，告訴自己，別再輕易走丟了。以後的事誰也不知道，起碼此刻，心還流動著，能有感動你、讓你感覺戀愛的小事，能與那些小事叨叨絮語、說說話，多麼好。


*沙龍客座嘉賓—法文旁白 林嘉欣 
亞洲知名演員、策展人、陶藝家；作品橫跨電影、舞台劇、配音，知名作品如《美國女孩》、《百日告別》、《親密》、《戀之風景》、《異度空間》、《男人四十》，並於2010年演出電影《戀人絮語》；近期傾心於陶藝作品，不時展覽。

title: Andrea Sannino - 1985
description:
1985 
(A.Sannino – A.Spenillo – M.Spenillo)

Ehi, abbassa un po’ il finestrino
Guarda quanta gente ca parla e cammina
Oggi nun se guardene cchiu, nun parlano cchiù, 
Pe’ furtuna ce stai tu
Ca me fai scurdà tutt’e pensieri
Sentimento d’ajere
Fore a nu’ chalet, pure sulo io e te, ‘na cassetta che gira

Senza se fermà, nun te vuò arritirà
‘o viento ‘nfaccia e ‘a voglia d’alluccà

E nun c’abbasta ‘na vita
Cu’ tte so’ sicuro ca ce ne vò n’ata
Nun è mai fernute, nun è mai passato
Pecchè ‘o tiempo mi si sempe tu, stasera
Dimme ca me vuò cchiù bene
Dimme ca è cchiù assaje d’ajere

Eh si, hai ragione tu
Ce sta ‘o sciopero ‘a cumana nun passa cchiù
Pure si ‘a partita sta pe’ ferni, ce fanno trasi, avviammece a’ppere
Si cchiù bella e ‘na bella canzone
Tu si cchiù ‘e Maradona
Senza nù pecchè, ce truvamme io e te dinte ‘a machina a’nnure

Senza ce fermà, nun te vuò arritirà
‘o viento ‘nfaccia e ‘a voglia d’alluccà

E nun c’abbasta ‘na vita
Cu’ tte so’ sicuro ca ce ne vò n’ata
Nun è mai fernute, nun è mai passato
Pecchè ‘o tiempo mi si sempe tu, stasera
Dimme ca me vuò cchiù bene

A nuie c’abbasta nu poco
‘a luce stutata, nu vaso arrubbato
‘na stanza cu ‘o cielo e ‘a radio appicciata
tiempo ca un conta niente cchiuù, stasera
dimme ca me vuò cchiù bene,
dimme ca è cchiu assaje da  ajere

…vedi quell’estate è finita
e ‘a vita mia è accumminciata.

title: Chiara Boni White | Milano, Sì Sposaitalia 2023 Fashion Show
description:
Chiara Boni, famosa designer del marchio ambasciatore del Made in Italy in tutto il mondo, prende parte per la prima volta a una manifestazione di settore: a Sì Sposaitalia Collezioni, in programma dal 14 al 17 aprile a Milano (Allianz MiCo), presenterà un’anteprima esclusiva della nuova collezione CHIARA BONI White. 

In un contesto raffinato che esalta l’esperienza e la maestria sartoriale dei migliori brand per abiti da sposa, sposo e cerimonia, Chiara Boni trova il suo spazio con il jersey iconico della linea La Petite Robe, creato con cura artigianale per abiti dal taglio armonioso, che accarezzano la silhouette.

Da sempre promotrice di una moda dal segno caratteristico, estremamente femminile e contemporanea, ripropone la stessa allure elegante e impeccabile negli abiti bianchi da sposa, che si legano a una certa atmosfera raffinata, declinata in toni moderni, chic e pratici anche nel giorno più importante. Tailleur lineari con piccoli dettagli luminosi e curati, abiti mini e midi in paillettes iridescenti, abiti lunghi con baschine e inserti floreali o sagomati e sinuosi: la proposta White di Chiara Boni prende ispirazione dalla passione e dall’affetto della stilista fiorentina per il suo giardino di fiori. 

Ricerca e qualità accomunano la collezione di Chiara Boni e la manifestazione milanese, insieme a creatività, stile italiano e tradizione, con uno sguardo contemporaneo e internazionale. Nella collezione sono i particolari a catturare il centro dell’attenzione: i delicati petali di un fiore, le pieghe inedite, le arricciature strategiche. L’emozione farà da fil rouge anche con l’esposizione del prezioso Abito Luce, progettato dall’Architetto Alessia Galimberti, che rappresenta un elemento di design distintivo.

title: Guru Money (Guru$$) - Official Music Video
description:
(western yoga satire)

Enjoyed the video?   Please subscribe and share!  The world needs more chakra bling, yo.            

What's the vibe, my celestial tribe?

Sada Sat Bing here, dropping a cosmic comedy bomb on y'all with "Guru Money"' a parody track that digs deep into the groove of the Western Yoga scene. Feel my flow?

We got a trippy music video that takes you on a journey, featuring a pure-soul earthling bewitched by the dazzling aura of a guru. Oh, and guess who's playing that guru? You vibin' with him right now, baby!

Don't forget to like, comment, share, and subscribe for more laughs and zen vibes. Namastay cool.

--Sada Sat Bing

https://pro.imdb.com/name/nm0664928 (reps & contact info -- professional inquiries only)

•☽────✧˖°˖☆˖°˖✧────☾•

DIRECTOR'S NOTES

Guru$$ started out as a joke. So many folks in Kundalini yoga had been given a name by Yogi Bhajan..."Gurmukh", "Sopurkh", "Sada Sat Kaur".

People asked my name. I said, "My name is Sada Sat BING" and got a laugh.

It became, "My name is Sada Sat BING, yoga's my thing."

So my new age satire life began, as I did spiritual comedy.

And then I saw what was happening in the yoga community. People think they will get the answers from one person and so they give away their power. Eventually, people, especially women, were exploited.  Not just Western Yoga.  Everywhere.

So I wrote a yoga comedy.

My little rhyme became a rap song.  Hip-hop yoga.  Comedy music about exploitation and ego, with a guru spitting old-school hip-hop. So many musical inspirations, from Slick Rick & Doug E. Fresh to Digable Planets.

Two years and three musicians later, Carl Burnett nailed it on the first pass.

We shot in 2017, again in 2018, and a little bit at the end in 2021 until we were satisfied that the story was clear. It was a lot of work but profoundly fulfilling.

Guru$$ is about a woman who tries to take a shortcut to enlightenment, gets caught up in the glitz, and ends up with nothing.

So yes, it is a comedy...

...and it is also a cautionary tale.

Since we started shooting, documentaries have been released about Bikram and Osho on Netflix, there an entire series on Vice about Yogi Bhajan and other yoga leaders who have exploited others, and last month, there was a Rolling Stone article about another one, Bentinho.

I hope you enjoy our labor of love…and maybe get the chorus stuck in your head.

title: Beparwah (Official Video) | Sidhant Kapoor X Ruskin Bond X The Sunshine Orchestra
description:
Sidhant Kapoor, a music composer, was so moved by a poetry called ‘Slum Children at Play’ by Ruskin Bond, that he drove up the hills of Mussoorie to meet the legendary writer and seek permission to put his words to music. On returning to Mumbai, Sidhant took notice of three street children and realised that they personify the emotions of the poetry. With this inspiration, Sidhant began his journey of composing his first ever single! He brought The Sunshine Orchestra, legendary composer A.R. Rahman's dream project, on board to perform the strings section. He wrote additional lyrics in Hindi and started painting the first few strokes of this composition. All through this process, he was inspired by the story of the three kids that taught him the true meaning of ‘Beparwah’!

'Beparwah' is available on all major platforms:

Imps of mischief,
Barefoot in the dust,
Grinning, mocking, even as
They beg you for a crust.
No angels these,
Just hungry eyes
And eager hands
To help you sympathise...

Beparwah...

They don’t want love,
They don’t seek pity,
They know there’s nothing
In this heartless city
But a kindred need
In those who strive
For power and pelf
Though only just alive!

Befikr inki subah, Befikr inki shaam,
Azaad parinde hai yeh, Beparwah inki udaan,
Na maange yeh zameen, inka toh aasmaan,
Azaad parinde hai yeh, Beparwah inki udaan.
Beparwah...

They know your guilt,
They’ll take your money,
And if you give too much
They’ll find you funny.
Because that’s what you are –
You’re just a joke –
Your life is soft
And theirs all grime and smoke.
And yet they shout and sing
And do not thank your giving,
You’ll fuss and fret through life
While they do all the living.

Beparwah...

Starring the talented Jimmy Roy, "Chal Chalein" takes you on a journey of uninterrupted youth love and entertainment. With no social media crowds or societal pressures, this song is all about having a good time and letting loose.

The song has great music by Chandan Mandal and the lyrics were written by Chandan Mandal and Sanjay Sen. It's going to be really popular with young people. The song comes out on May 15th, 2023, and it will be available to watch and listen on GrooveNexus. Don't miss out on the fun!

蒼穹盛開的藍色花朵，
面具底下是難以捉摸；
即便向著刺也要伸手，
只為她笑容不為什麼。

「塔莉亞」是希臘九大繆思女神之ㄧ，手握「花與面具」。將充滿詩意的象徵元素作為歌曲創作靈感，敘述男孩仰望著如女神般心儀的她，就算明知這份美麗藏著危險與刺，也心甘情願為之臣服。

新生代最強唱作團體U:NUS，於《Reborn To be Alive》巡迴Showcase第二站 ── 台北，驚喜發表首支R&B全創作單曲《塔莉亞》（Thalia），透過精心編排的舞台表演與性感舞蹈，首度嘗試成熟魅力的表演風格，引起全場粉絲的熱烈迴響、陷入瘋狂。《塔莉亞》作為U:NUS發表的第三首作品，團員透過細膩的歌詞和與過往截然不同的曲風，展現更加純熟的唱腔與聲音表情，編曲元素更加入具千禧年代感性的電吉他solo與留聲機效果，加上男孩們如在耳邊溫柔呢喃的說唱，打造如同文藝愛情電影般的浪漫氛圍歌曲。

風格多變的U:NUS，再次突破了音樂創作的界限、為音樂之路添上嶄新色彩，也讓人更加期待未來他們將帶來什麼樣的驚喜！

                                         Cuando te vi

“Hola”, dijiste tu y parecía un poema, era de día pero había estrellas,
Mi corazón salto, como si de una te reconociera.

“hola”, te dije y también te pedí la hora, fue la excusa mas tonta pero ahora, te tengo para mi, y solo para mi es lo que importa.

Esto parece un sueño, pero es tan real.

Cuando yo te vi, no tuve duda sabia que eras tú, a quien tanto espere, y el cielo es mas azul, desde que estas tu.

Cuando yo te vi, sentí que no debía dejarte escapar, y ahora no pienso en nada solamente en ti, supe que es vivir, cuando te vi.

Y tu mirada, tu mirada me hizo tanto bien, como el sol al día como el agua pa' la sed, la cura para mis heridas, es verte en mi pecho dormida, yo le doy gracias a la vida por tenerte aquí.

Cuando yo te vi, no tuve duda sabia que eras tú, a quien tanto espere, y el cielo es mas azul, desde que estas tu.

Cuando yo te vi, sentí que no debía dejarte escapar, y ahora no pienso en nada solamente en ti, supe que es vivir, cuando te vi.

El video fue grabado en la ciudad de Madrid, los protagonistas son Rammar Rivero y la modelo Yerardy Montoya.a

title: Ep-03 | Extempore Musical Journeys | Talk Show With Paras Ft.Vinod Katoch | Two For Joy
description:
#ExtemporeMusicalJourney #podcast #guitarist 

►Podcast With Paras Ft.Vinod Katoch (Full Episode)

Welcome to Extempore Musical Journeys! I'm excited to introduce you to this unique and exciting project created in collaboration with Two for Joy Studio. Extempore Musical Journeys takes you on a musical voyage like no other, where the destination and musical style are unknown, and the journey is completely improvised. Each episode features talented musicians who come together to create something truly special in the moment. This project is all about pushing boundaries and exploring the unknown, and we can't wait for you to come along for the ride. Get ready for an unforgettable musical experience that will leave you wanting more.
A Pantellisense Production!

—————————————————————————————————————————————— 
Subscribe to Our Official YouTube Channel : https://www.youtube.com/@TWOFORJOY
—————————————————————————————————————————————— 

►Podcast With Paras Ft.Vinod Katoch (Full Episode)

Episode 3 of Extempore Musical Journeys with Paras and Vinod takes us on a journey to discover finger style guitar. Paras starts off by explaining the basics of finger style guitar and demonstrates a few techniques.

Vinod then picks up his guitar and they start playing Mohit Chauhan's popular song 'Boondein' in finger style. The music is soothing and mesmerizing as their fingers move effortlessly on the strings, producing beautiful melodies.

As they continue playing, Paras and Vinod share their experiences with finger style guitar and how it has opened up new musical avenues for them. They also discuss the importance of practice and perseverance in mastering the technique.

The episode ends with a soulful rendition of 'Boondein' in finger style, leaving the viewers mesmerized and wanting more of such melodious and informative musical journeys.

title: Franz Liszt, Liebestraum - Simon Bürki
description:
Album available on the 19th of May, pre-order now. 
👉 https://aparte.lnk.to/reminiscence

Né en 2000, lauréat de nombreux concours internationaux, Simon Bürki étudie actuellement avec Sergei Babayan à la Juilliard School de New York. C’est avec Rachmaninoff – dont on célèbre les 150 ans en 2023 –, Scriabine, Tchaïkovski, Liszt et Schumann qu’il fait ses débuts au disque. Ce premier enregistrement réunit plusieurs des ténébreuses Études-Tableaux et des Préludes de Rachmaninoff, deux Études de Scriabine, ainsi qu’une sélection de transcriptions et de courtes pièces, affirmant d’emblée les affinités de Simon Bürki. Dans ces miniatures (post-)romantiques, le pianiste se démarque par sa virtuosité sans faille et une élégance sobre, qui laissent toute la place à son jeu flamboyant et intense.


Born in 2000, Simon Bürki has won many international competitions. Currently studying at the Juilliard School, New York, with Sergei Babayan. His début recording features works by Rachmaninov – 2023 marks the 150th anniversary of the composer’s birth – and Scriabin, Tchaikovsky, Liszt and Schumann. The programme confirms Simon Bürki’s affinities, with some of Rachmaninov’s sombre Études-Tableaux and Préludes, together with two Études by Scriabin, and a selection of transcriptions and short pieces. In these (post-)Romantic miniatures, the young pianist demonstrates his outstanding virtuosity and sober elegance, as well as the exciting flamboyancy and intensity of his playing.

Taken off the album "The Fall Of The Shires" (August 18th, 2023)
🎧 Stream, get it here: https://oblivionprotocol.afr.link/thefalloftheshiresYT

Mastermind Richard West explains: "At the end of »Legends Of The Shires,« the protagonist considers a number of possible futures ("maybe a painter, a guide, a clerk, a maker, or maybe a writer, a king, a star, a fighter"). So the sequel tells the story of him becoming the king and the consequences of that choice. In the opening song, he decides that the only way to control the population is to suppress and control them, so the shires become a much darker place."

The first digital single, 'Forests In The Fallout,' is told from the perspective of the suppressed people and is the perfect introduction to this new progressive metal masterpiece.

title: Only a Dream (from the film "Five Moments") - Ted Ganger
description:
This performance is taken from the award-winning short film "Five Moments," soon to be released in its entirety here on YouTube.

Lyrics and music by Ted Ganger
Magdalena Herfurtner (Madil Hardis), voice
(https://www.youtube.com/c/MadilHardis)
Ted Ganger, piano

#MagdalenaHerfurtner #MadilHardis
#TedGanger

You might also like this song sung (and played) as a "Song of the Week" by Ted Ganger.
https://youtu.be/XP3AvWA6boo

ONLY A DREAM

I dreamed that I lay beside her,                                                                                                                   And we were as we used to be.                                                                                                                    But somehow I couldn't believe it,                                                                                                                 And struggled and tried to get free. 
I cried out: I know I'm dreaming.                                                                                                                 She laughed and kept pulling me in.                                                                                                                I fought my way up to the surface                                                                                                                 And woke, full of what had not been.
 
For that couldn't really happen,                                                                                                                     No matter how things might seem,                                                                                                              So go back to sleep, yes, go back to sleep, just go back to sleep -                                                           It was only a dream.

I dreamed she was going to leave me,                                                                                                        She told me I wasn't the one.                                                                                                                       She smoked on a bench in the moonlight                                                                                                  And spoke what she'd already done.
She thought I should hear it directly,                                                                                                          And now she'd get on with her life.                                                                                                                 I'm still sitting there in the moonlight                                                                                                            And still feel the twist of the knife.

But that never really happened,                                                                                                                      No matter how things might seem,                                                                                                                                  So go back to sleep, yes, go back to sleep, just go back to sleep -                                                                                                It was only a dream.


I dreamed that we once were strangers,                                                                                                          Two souls that had gone astray.                                                                                                                                         We both led the life of the lonely,                                                                                                                                                             And both came from far away.
We knew it would not be easy,                                                                                                                       But felt it was destined to be.                                                                                                                                         So I sent my heart on its journey,                                                                                                                                                 And she shared her secrets with me.

It may be that never happened,                                                                                                                      No matter how things might seem,                                                                                                                                  But go back to sleep, yes, go back to sleep, just go back to sleep -                                                                                            Though it's only a dream.

In season 2 of Supply Chain Transformed, we look at how the world is tackling new and ever-present challenges in global logistics. Recent years have shown how much risk truly exists between point A and B, and in this season, we’ll explore how technology is poised to provide visibility and insight into where risk lies, and how to ensure nothing catches us off-guard again.

title: 『마틸다』 - 세기와 장르를 뛰어넘어 사랑받는책 읽는 소녀 영웅 │6분 안에 듣는 고전문학 [6분 클래식]
description:
로알드 달, 『마틸다』

1916년 영국 웨일스에서 태어난 작가 로알드 달은 『찰리와 로콜릿 공장』 등의 작품으로 널리 알려져 있는데요. 석유회사 직원, 전투기 조종사 등을 거쳐 뒤늦게 작가의 길로 들어섰지만 기발하고 독특한 상상력으로 많은 작품을 남겼습니다. 오늘 소개해드린 『마틸다』를 비롯해 여러 작품이 영화나 뮤지컬로 창작되면서 더 큰 인기를 누리기도 했고요. 『마틸다』는 로알드 달이 1990년 세상을 뜨기 전에 마지막으로 쓴 아동 장편소설이기도 합니다.
어렸을 적부터 비범했던 소녀 마틸다는 부모의 방치와 무관심에도 불구하고 홀로 책을 읽어나가며 자신의 세계를 키워 갑니다. 도서관에서 학교에 입학하기도 전에 영문학의 고전을 두루 섭렵한 마틸다는 자신을 좀처럼 인정하려 들지 않고 차별과 억압을 일삼는 부모, 특히 아버지에게 유쾌한 복수를 해가며 드디어 학교에 입학하게 되는데요. 일찍이 마틸다의 천재성을 알아본 담임 하니 선생님은 마틸다를 상급반에 진학시켜야 한다고 건의하지만 부모의 무시는 물론이거니와 폭군과도 같은 트런치불 교장에 의해 그 제안은 묵살되고 맙니다. 겸손하고 성숙한 마틸다는 그러한 상황 속에서도 자신을 지키면서 특별한 능력을 발견하게 되는데요. 그것은 집중해서 무언가를 응시할 때 물체를 움직일 수 있는 힘이었습니다. 그 힘을 통해 마틸다는 하니 선생님을, 또 자기 자신을 구해내고 새로운 삶을 시작하게 됩니다.
『마틸다』는 이야기를 한껏 흥미롭게 만드는 로알드 달의 장기가 유감없이 발휘된 작품이라고 할 수 있습니다. 일흔을 넘긴 말년의 나이에 작가는 천재 소녀 마틸다를 통해 삶의 희망을 선물하고자 했던 것 같습니다. 어린 여자아이를 무시하고 차별하는 아버지, 또 아이들을 억압하고 힘으로 제압하려는 탐욕스러운 교장 등에게 통쾌한 복수와 처벌을 선사하면서 작가는 결국 정의롭고 진실된 사람이 승리하는 모습을 보여주고 있는데요. 그것이 특히 책과 문학 작품을 통해 이루어진다는 점도 주목할 만합니다. 찰스 디킨스, 샬럿 브론테, 제인 오스틴, 토마스 하디, 어니스트 헤밍웨이, 존 스타인백, 조지프 콘래드, 러디어드 키플링, 윌리엄 포크너, 조지 오웰 등 걸작을 남긴 영문학 작가들을 두루 언급하면서 작가는 그런 “책을 조금이라도 읽는다면, 인생에는 사람을 속이거나 텔레비전을 보는 것보다 더 많은 것이 담겨 있다는 것을 발견하게 될” 것이라고 역설하고 있습니다. 아마도 작가 로알드 달은 여러 대중 매체의 영향으로 책과 문학의 가치가 점점 사라져가지 않을까 우려했던 것 같은데요. 역설적이게도 여러 작품이 영화나 뮤지컬로 재창작되어 큰 인기를 끌기도 했고 여전히 그의 소설은 독자들의 큰 사랑을 받고 있으니 작가가 이러한 광경을 목도했다면 어떤 반응을 보였을지 궁금해지기도 합니다.
올해 초 영국에서는 로알드 달의 작품들을 새로 출간하면서 시대에 맞지 않는 차별적 표현들을 수정해서 논란이 되기도 했습니다. 출판사와 유족 측은 편견을 조장할 수 있는 비하나 혐오의 언어들을 고쳐서 더 많은 사람들이 작가의 작품을 즐길 수 있도록 했다는 취지로 설명을 했는데요. 여러 독자들을 비롯해 몇몇 작가들은 이 수정에 대해 강한 반대의 뜻을 나타내기도 했습니다. 결국 출판사는 수정본과 원본을 동시에 출간하는 것으로 사태를 정리하였는데, 작가가 생존해 있었다면 어떤 결정을 내렸을까 생각도 해보게 됩니다. 어찌 되었든 로알드 달의 작품들이 전 세계의 독자들로부터 사랑받고 있다는 점은 분명한 것 같습니다. 여러 작품들을 다양한 방법으로 접할 수 있는 만큼 이 기회에 로알드 달의 기발한 세계에 빠져 보시기를 바랍니다.

title: Architect-Artist Innovates CG Film Production with CC AccuRIG, Redshift SSS and iClone
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/auto-rig.html London-based architect Kay John Yim has set his sights on his next ambitious animation project, "Masquerade," following the completion of his previous works "Ballerina" and "Kagura." Yim is sparing no effort in creating this new debut short CG film and takes us through his character creation workflow in an in-depth video. He demonstrates how he streamlined the process by integrating the auto-rig features in Character Creator 4 (CC) and working with CC AccuRIG, Cinema 4D, and Redshift Random Walk SSS.

Yim's use of the cutting-edge Redshift software (version 3.4.06) paired with the streamlined CC-iClone character workflow synergistically optimizes the creation of stunning, realistic SSS (subsurface scattering) effects, minimizing the time required for rendering and lighting adjustments.

The mesmerizing vanishing effect of the star's cloak is created using Yim's advanced Cinema 4D setup, ultimately revealing her identity and opulent ball gown. His signature style of infusing each character with captivating charm and infusing glamorous sets with cinematic effects shines through in "Masquerade."

Additionally, Yim's utilization of the Edit Motion Layer feature, available exclusively in iCone 8, seamlessly blends motion data from Actocore and Xsens, resulting in his distinct and genuine animation style. In an age where text-to-image AI is ascending, Yim's work serves as a testament to human creativity, honoring the pursuit of art and provoking contemplation on its very essence.

"Masquerade" was featured in the 2023 Cinema 4D and Redshift showreel.
Access the article now for more Pro Tips and CGI resources from Kay John Yim. https://magazine.reallusion.com/2023/05/02/architect-artist-innovates-cg-film-production-with-cc-accurig-redshift-sss-and-iclone/

title: Lead Generation for Private Jet Industry & Understanding Customer Qualification
description:
Private/charter jets industry is a niche market that caters to a high-end clientele seeking luxury travel experiences. Understanding this industry can help in lead generation and customer qualification. Here are some key aspects to consider:

1. Target market: Private/charter jets are primarily used by high-net-worth individuals, corporate executives, celebrities, and government officials. Therefore, understanding the demographics and psychographics of this target market can help in lead generation and customer qualification.

2. Services and amenities: Private/charter jets offer a range of services and amenities such as personalized in-flight catering, luxury interiors, and advanced entertainment systems. Understanding the specific needs and preferences of the target market can help in tailoring the services and amenities to attract and retain customers.

3. Price and value: Private/charter jets are expensive, and pricing varies based on the type of aircraft, distance, and duration of the flight. Understanding the value proposition of the service and communicating it effectively to potential customers can help in generating leads and qualifying customers.

4. Reputation and referrals: Reputation and referrals play a crucial role in the private/charter jets industry. Positive reviews and referrals from satisfied customers can help in generating new leads and qualifying potential customers.

5. Industry regulations: The private/charter jets industry is highly regulated, and compliance with regulations is critical for lead generation and customer qualification. Understanding and complying with industry regulations can help build trust and credibility with potential customers.

6. Compliance: The private/charter jets industry is highly regulated, and it's important to comply with regulations when advertising on Facebook and Google. Be transparent about pricing, disclose any fees or surcharges, and avoid making misleading claims.

title: Shopify Pricing | What is Shopify? | Shopify Website | E-commerce | Shopify Tutorial
description:
Shopify Pricing | What is Shopify? | Shopify Website | E-commerce | Shopify Tutorial

https://profiletree.com/ecommerce-web-design-agency/

Welcome to this ProfileTree video
In this video, we will explain what Shopify pricing plans are available for you to choose from and how you can build and use a website using the eCommerce platform for your own business.

Shopify is an e-commerce platform that allows individuals and businesses to create their own online stores and sell products or services online. It was founded in 2004 and has since grown to become one of the most popular e-commerce platforms in the world. 

Shopify offers several pricing plans that cater to businesses of different sizes and needs. Here are the different Shopify pricing plans and their benefits:

Basic Shopify - $29 per month: This plan is designed for small businesses just starting out with an online store. It includes all the essential features needed to launch a basic online store, including unlimited products, 24/7 customer support, and the ability to accept credit card payments.

Shopify - $79 per month: This plan includes all the features of Basic Shopify, plus more advanced features such as gift cards, professional reports, and the ability to create discount codes. It's a good option for growing businesses with higher sales volumes.

Advanced Shopify - $299 per month: This plan includes all the features of Shopify, plus more advanced features such as advanced report building, third-party calculated shipping rates, and the ability to customize your checkout process. It's ideal for large businesses with high sales volumes and complex needs.

Shopify Plus - Custom pricing: This is the most advanced plan offered by Shopify, designed for enterprise-level businesses with complex needs. It includes all the features of Advanced Shopify, plus personalized support, advanced security features, and custom integrations.

The benefits of Shopify pricing plans include:

Scalability: As your business grows and your needs change, you can upgrade your Shopify plan to access more features and support.

Flexibility: Shopify pricing plans offer flexibility to businesses of different sizes and budgets, with plans designed for small, medium, and large businesses.

Ease of use: Shopify is easy to set up and use, with an intuitive interface and a wide range of apps and integrations available to extend the platform's functionality.

Reliability: Shopify offers reliable hosting, security, and uptime, ensuring that your online store is always available to customers.

Support: Shopify offers 24/7 customer support via phone, email, and live chat, as well as a comprehensive knowledge base and community forums.

Overall, Shopify pricing plans offer a wide range of features and support to help businesses of all sizes launch and grow their online stores.

Chris Jarvis is known by many millionaire business owners and billionaire families as the guy who sees differently.

After 25 years of working with the super affluent, he discovered that there are countless ways to be successful, but only one path for each of us to find happiness and fulfillment.  

If you seek better health, increased wealth, stronger relationships, a deeper sense of purpose, or more fun in your life, then you want to find your “wild factor” to help you get unstuck, uncaged, and be free to Go Wild!  

If you are feeling uninspired, uncomfortable, or unfulfilled, then this talk may be the key to set you free to do what you were meant to do — without fear, guilt, or further hesitation.  

By the end of this talk, you will understand how a preoccupation with “surviving” sabotages our chances of “thriving” in our personal life and in our professional life.

Chris has enjoyed high highs and endured low lows.  Now he shares what he learned the hard way, helping seemingly happy and successful people escape the traps they set for themselves so they can find peace, laughter, and fulfillment. Chris’ greatest discovery came from years of hiking and a month on safari in Africa.  

The author of seventeen books and board member for a business school and medical school, Chris loves to teach.  He offers keynote speeches, strategy and innovation sessions, executive and team retreats, and “giraffe selling“ training program. With individual clients, Chris helps entrepreneurs and family offices handle their most complicated emotional and financial challenges to ensure successful transitions and exit strategies to generate greater leverage and more meaningful impact.  

Elevate Your Perspective.
See a Better Path.

title: Manali Tour | Part-3 | Atal Tunnel | Highest Tunnel in the World | Manali to Lahaul | Lahaul in May
description:
Lahaul district is connected to Manali through the Rohtang Pass. Lahaul Valley of Himachal Pradesh in the northern part of the country has become the most popular tourist destination of Himachal due to its easy approach after the opening of the Atal Tunnel, Rohtang. Lahaul valley is just 33 km from Manali along the Manali-Leh highway. The valley starts from the northern end of the Atal tunnel. The atal tunnel is the bridge between Manali and Lahaul. Before the tunnel, Lahaul was reachable via Rohtang pass. Rohtang top, 51 km from Manali, is the boundary of Manali and Lahaul valley.
Atal Tunnel (also known as Rohtang Tunnel), named after former Prime Minister of India, Atal Bihari Vajpayee is a highway tunnel built under the Rohtang Pass. At a length of 9.02 km, it is the highest highway single-tube tunnel above 10,000 feet (3,048 m) in the world. The tunnel reduces the travel time and overall distance between Manali and Keylong on the way to Leh. The route, which previously went through Gramphu, was 116 km (72.1 mi) long and took 5 to 6 hours in good conditions. Prime Minister Narendra Modi inaugurated the Atal Tunnel in Manali, Himachal Pradesh on 3 October 2020.

title: Origin of Life: You Can't Trust Everything You Hear (Long Story Short, Ep. 9)
description:
Can you trust everything you hear about the origin of life? The short answer is “No.” Many popular science expositors overstate the evidence for the natural, chemical origin of life and promote gross misinformation to the public on this topic. This video reviews popular claims made about the origin of life and shows why they are contradicted by the evidence, misleading, or flat out false.

This is the sixth of several episodes about the origin of life presented as part of the Long Story Short series. If you enjoyed this one, you will like all the others. Clever, humorous, substantive, brief, “Long Story Short," is an occasional video series that compresses key points in the debate between Darwinism and intelligent design into a very welcome format: concise, accessible, and funny.   https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLR8eQzfCOiS0AfFPsMAUYr_VVkpU13uv9

title: S2:A6 | VÄX UPP FÖR F*N | OSCAR ZIA OCH MARKUS TORGEBY FLYR STRESSEN OCH LEVER LIVET I VILDMARKEN
description:
Skulle du byta ut din ångest mot att bo utomhus i vildmarken i fyra år? Det gjorde Markus Torgeby när livet svalde honom levande så att han knappt kunde andas. I det här avsnittet provar Oscar på att sova ute i skogen för att ta reda på om det kan vara ett botemedel mot konsekvenserna av det moderna livets stora faror. Oscar och Markus pratar om att odla sin inre trädgård och diskuterar om en löptur verkligen kan hjälpa mot stress och ångest. 

Om serien
I andra säsongen av Väx upp för f*n är artisten Oscar Zia ingen newbie på det jordnära livet längre. Han fortsätter fråga sig hur bra vi mår av att leva med hämtmat, doomscrolling och flygresor kors och tvärs. Han vill stanna upp, göra tvärtom och gräva där han står. Med hjälp av sina nyförvärvade kunskaper om växter har han bytt ut odlingarna på fönsterbrädan till ett trädgårdsland på torpet. Vid det röda huset i skogen får han besök av personer som kan lära honom allt om hur han kan lyckas bli självförsörjande ute på landet. 

Medverkande
Oscar Zia
Markus Torgeby

title: The benefits of writing by hand | Katie McCleary | TEDxEustis
description: Leadership professor and writing and consciousness expert, Katie McCleary, MFA, offers the benefits of writing by hand for all ages. Based on more than 25 years of writing with thousands of people, McCleary offers insights into the science of handwriting and how it can easily improve your focus, elevate your thinking, deliver the “sticky factor” to retain new learning, and create more meaningful, resonate connections. So, go ahead, let go of the grammar police, write in your messy unique font, and see what bubbles up when you try slow and write by hand. Katie McCleary is an author, changemaker, professor of leadership and a lover of people. Earning her MFA, in Writing and Consciousness, led to her belief that handwriting is a path to transform the self, communities and the world. She is also the coauthor of Bridge the Gap, which Inc. named 1 of 3 business books to read in 2022. As the founder of the nonprofit, 916 Ink, Katie has helped more than 4500 young people become confident authors who know the power of the pen. Mashable.com named her 1 of 15 “Real Miss Americas” for her career in uplifting communities. She is the host of NPR CapRadio’s leadership podcast, “The Drive.” Katie teaches in the Masters of Nonprofit Leadership at Pacific University. Her work has appeared in Forbes, PBS, Shondaland, Thrive, Apple News, and Hip Mama. She lives with 2 children, 15 chickens, 1 talkative parrot, and other furry creatures in California. She is handwriting her next book: A Biomythography of Our Being: What We Become when We Write. This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at https://www.ted.com/tedx

title: Trabaja mientras los demás duermen, el Reality Show de Jeremías Martorell en Tulum. Episodio #1
description:
Extrema; apasionante; sorprendente; dinámica; multifacética. 

Así es la vida de Jeremías Martorell, empresario e inversionista de los Estados Unidos y CEO de Martorell's Group, quien ha consolidado una experiencia de crecimientos, aprendizajes, logros, tropiezos y momentos inolvidables durante casi tres décadas de recorrido profesional. 

En este, su primer reality show, el Vlog "Trabaja mientras los demás duermen", Jeremías Martorell nos presenta una bitácora emocionante de su visita a la ciudad de Tulum, en México, en compañía de una parte de su familia y compañeros de su conglomerado empresarial, Martorell's Group. 

Se trata de una mezcla explosiva de diversión, turismo, negocios y aventuras inesperadas, que te cautivarán en cada minuto del camino.

"Trabaja mientras los demás duermen" es más que un Vlog, es más que un reality show, es más que un slogan... "Trabaja mientras los demás duermen" es una filosofía de vida que nos enseña la importancia de aprovechar el tiempo al máximo; que nos recuerda cuántas oportunidades maravillosas nos rodean; y que nos confirma el valor de luchar con tenacidad y compromiso por nuestros sueños.

¡Acompáñanos a descubrir Tulum y a adentrarnos más en la vida de Jeremías Martorell!

title: Short Film "The way back home" ｜ショートフィルム『海の見える街で』本編（英語字幕付き）
description:
(Japanese Below) 
Academy Awards® accredited festival 
Short Shorts Film Festival & Asia  

FY 2022 Japan Cultural Expo Project Presented and Co-presented by Japan Arts Council and Agency for Cultural Affairs, Government of Japan
　
Short Film "The way back home"

24:52 / 2023 / Japan
Writter / Director / Editor: Karin Miyagi
Cast: Rintaro Mizusawa, Takara Sakumoto, Teruhiro Tanaka, Sora Shiota, Kyanhitomi, Yoshi Sako and Masato Hagiwara
Original Story "The Two of Us, in a Town with a View of the Sea" by Kento Norikane

Synopsis:
Childhood friends Hinata and Hayato are training hard in kendo for their final high school inter-high school competition.
One day, Hinata is scouted by an entertainment agency. This causes a rift in their relationship.
The film depicts these two young boys who grow up to be adults while still carrying the pain & doubts from their youth.     

In 2022, the Japan Expo project was inaugurated to draw on the essence of cultures and tales that lie dormant in various areas of Japan and condense them into short stories. Short stories set in Iwate, Shizuoka & Fukuoka Prefectures were submitted & selected. 
At the SSFF & ASIA 2022 Fall Festival held in October 2022, a panel discussion was held with the invited writers of the stories. In addition, the short story "The Two of Us, in a Town with a View of the Sea" by Kento Norikane which was inspired by the novel "Konjiki Yasha" by writer Ozaki Kōyō, a famed author whose statue is in Atami City, has been adapted into a short film written & directed by Karin Miyagi and will be distributed worldwide through online screenings.

Official web site:
https://www.shortshorts.org/japanculturalexpo/en/creation-of-stories-all-around-japan/

原作：「海の見える街で私たち」#乘金顕斗

〇あらすじ：
高校最後のインターハイに向け、剣道の練習に励んでいた幼馴染の日向と颯人。
ある日、日向が芸能事務所にスカウトされたことがきっかけで二人の関係に亀裂が生じ始め…。
傷つき、悩みながら大人へと成長していく二人の少年の姿を描く。

〇概要：
令和4年度の日本博事業では、日本各地に眠る文化や物語のエッセンスを抽出し短編小説に昇華するプロジェクトを実施し、岩手県、静岡県、福岡県を舞台にした3つのショートストーリーが生まれました。
2022年10月に開催されたSSFF & ASIA 2022 秋の国際短編映画祭では、執筆を行った作家の方々をお招きしてのパネルディスカッションの開催を行ったほか、#静岡県 #熱海市に銅像がある事でも知られる #尾崎紅葉 の小説「#金色夜叉」をモチーフとした短編小説「海の見える街で私たち」（乘金顕斗著）が、宮城夏鈴監督によりショートフィルム化され、オンラインを通じて世界配信致します。

title: The 8 Flow Accelerators at the LPM level
description:
Odile Moreau,  Strategic Advisor and SPCT from Scaled Agile
visited the We Are Movement Lean Portfolio Management meetup in Stockholm. Odile shared how to apply the eight flow accelerators to pursue perfection in the collaborations in Lean Portfolio Management. 

The eight Flow Accelerators are:
1. Visualize and limit WIP
2. Address bottlenecks
3. Minimize handoffs and dependencies
4. Get faster feedback
5. Work in smaller batches
6. Reduce queue lengths
7. Optimize time ‘in the zone’
8. Remediate legacy policies and practices

title: Gukesh D vs Vladimir Kramnik, Nodirbek Abdusattorov vs Parham Maghsoodloo | Day 6 Armageddon
description:
Welcome to the most star-spangled showdown in the Armageddon Championship Series: Asia & Oceania featuring Vladimir Kramnik, Gukesh D, Yangyi Yu, Nodirbek Abdusattorov, Daniil Dubov, Vidit Gujrathi, Karthikeyan Murali, and Parham Maghsoodloo.

Tune in live on April 7 at 20:00 CET for chess heroes under intense time pressure with a real-time heartbeat and calorie-burned level as they race across the board for the chance to win €50,000 and two spots in Grand Finale. 

Commentators GM Jan Gustafsson and IM Jovanka Houska will do their best to keep up.

Armageddon Championship Series is a season of ultra-fast blitz tournaments with continental qualifiers and a Grand Finale event. The Series consists of seven-day double-elimination tournaments (if a player loses a match, he or she can still win the tournament and is eliminated after a second loss). Matches consist of two blitz games (3 minutes plus a 2-second move increment) and, if necessary, an Armageddon (5 minutes for White, 4 minutes for Black). There are two matches per day. The top two players of each event secure two places in the Grand Finale. All games are broadcast live from the Armageddon Studio in Berlin, and the total event prize fund of the Series is €460 000. The Series is organized by World Chess.
